---
// 어드민 (비밀번호 보호) — 대시보드 · 콘텐츠 관리(에디터) · 통계
import '../styles/global.css';
import { SITE } from '../consts.ts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <title>관리자 · {SITE.title}</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <!-- 에디터 미리보기용 마크다운 파서 -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/marked@14/marked.min.js" defer></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- 로그인 -->
    <section id="login" class="login">
      <form id="loginForm" class="card">
        <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <h1>관리자</h1>
        <p class="muted">{SITE.title} · 대시보드 / 콘텐츠 / 통계</p>
        <input id="pw" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호" autocomplete="current-password" />
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">들어가기</button>
        <p id="loginErr" class="err" hidden>비밀번호가 올바르지 않습니다.</p>
        <p id="localNote" class="muted small" hidden>로컬 미리보기: 아무 값이나 입력하면 샘플 데이터로 열립니다.</p>
      </form>
    </section>

    <!-- 어드민 셸 -->
    <main id="shell" class="shell" hidden>
      <header class="topbar">
        <div class="container-wide inner">
          <div class="left">
            <a href="/" class="brand" target="_blank">{SITE.title} <span class="ext">↗</span></a>
            <nav class="tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="어드민 메뉴">
              <button class="tab active" data-view="dashboard">대시보드</button>
              <button class="tab" data-view="content">콘텐츠</button>
              <button class="tab" data-view="stats">통계</button>
            </nav>
          </div>
          <div class="right">
            <span id="sampleBadge" class="badge" hidden>샘플 데이터</span>
            <button id="logout" class="btn-utility">로그아웃</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- ═══ 대시보드 ═══ -->
      <section id="view-dashboard" class="view container-wide">
        <div class="kpis six">
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">오늘 조회수</span><span class="k-val" id="dToday">–</span></div>
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">어제 조회수</span><span class="k-val" id="dYesterday">–</span></div>
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">누적 조회수</span><span class="k-val" id="dTotal">–</span></div>
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">오늘 방문자</span><span class="k-val" id="dVToday">–</span></div>
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">어제 방문자</span><span class="k-val" id="dVYesterday">–</span></div>
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">누적 방문자</span><span class="k-val" id="dVTotal">–</span></div>
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">이메일 구독자</span><span class="k-val" id="dSubs">–</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>최근 30일 추이</h2>
          <div id="dChart" class="chart"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid2">
          <div class="panel">
            <h2>인기글 <span class="muted small">최근 30일</span></h2>
            <ol id="dTopPosts" class="ranklist"></ol>
          </div>
          <div class="panel">
            <h2>유입 채널 <span class="muted small">최근 30일</span></h2>
            <div id="dRefTypes" class="bars"></div>
            <h3 class="sub">유입 사이트</h3>
            <div id="dTopRef" class="rows"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ═══ 콘텐츠 관리 ═══ -->
      <section id="view-content" class="view container-wide" hidden>
        <div class="content-head">
          <h2>글 관리 <span id="postCount" class="muted small"></span></h2>
          <div class="content-tools">
            <input id="postSearch" type="search" placeholder="제목·파일명 검색" aria-label="글 검색" />
            <button id="newPost" class="btn btn-primary small-btn">+ 새 글</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p id="contentNote" class="muted small" hidden>
          로컬 미리보기에서는 콘텐츠 관리를 사용할 수 없습니다 (배포 환경 + GITHUB_TOKEN 필요).
        </p>
        <div id="postList" class="postlist panel"></div>

        <!-- 에디터 -->
        <div id="editor" class="editor" hidden>
          <div class="editor-head">
            <div>
              <h2 id="edTitle">글 편집</h2>
              <p class="muted small" id="edSlug"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="editor-actions">
              <span id="seoHints" class="seohints"></span>
              <button id="edDraft" class="btn-utility" type="button" title="초안/발행 전환">상태</button>
              <button id="edPvToggle" class="btn-utility" type="button">미리보기</button>
              <button id="edDelete" class="btn-utility danger" type="button" hidden>삭제</button>
              <button id="edCancel" class="btn-utility">목록으로</button>
              <button id="edSave" class="btn btn-primary small-btn">저장</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="toolbar" role="toolbar" aria-label="서식 도구">
            <button type="button" data-md="h2">제목</button>
            <button type="button" data-md="h3">소제목</button>
            <button type="button" data-md="bold" title="굵게"><b>B</b></button>
            <button type="button" data-md="italic" title="기울임"><i>I</i></button>
            <button type="button" data-md="link">링크</button>
            <button type="button" data-md="ul">목록</button>
            <button type="button" data-md="quote">인용</button>
            <button type="button" data-md="code">코드</button>
            <span class="tb-sep"></span>
            <button type="button" data-md="table">표</button>
            <button type="button" data-md="mermaid">다이어그램</button>
          </div>

          <div class="split" id="edSplit">
            <textarea id="edBody" spellcheck="false"></textarea>
            <div id="edPreview" class="prose preview" aria-label="미리보기"></div>
          </div>
          <p id="edMsg" class="muted small" hidden></p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ═══ 통계 ═══ -->
      <section id="view-stats" class="view container-wide" hidden>
        <div class="stats-head">
          <h2>방문 통계</h2>
          <div class="range" role="group" aria-label="기간">
            <button data-days="7">7일</button>
            <button data-days="30" class="active">30일</button>
            <button data-days="90">90일</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpis">
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">방문자</span><span class="k-val" id="kVisitors">–</span></div>
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">페이지뷰</span><span class="k-val" id="kViews">–</span></div>
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">일평균 방문자</span><span class="k-val" id="kAvg">–</span></div>
          <div class="kpi"><span class="k-label">방문자당 페이지</span><span class="k-val" id="kPer">–</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h2>일별 추이 <span class="muted small" id="rangeLabel"></span></h2>
          <div id="chart" class="chart"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid2">
          <div class="panel"><h2>인기 글 · 경로</h2><div id="paths" class="rows"></div></div>
          <div class="panel">
            <h2>유입 경로</h2>
            <div id="refTypes" class="bars"></div>
            <h3 class="sub">유입 사이트</h3>
            <div id="topRef" class="rows"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid2">
          <div class="panel"><h2>기기</h2><div id="devices" class="bars"></div></div>
          <div class="panel"><h2>국가</h2><div id="countries" class="rows"></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer class="foot container-wide muted small">
        자체 수집 애널리틱스(비식별) · 에디터 저장은 GitHub 커밋 · SETUP.md 참고
      </footer>
    </main>

    <script is:inline>
      (function () {
        var KEY = 'coa_admin_key';
        var isLocal = ['localhost', '127.0.0.1'].indexOf(location.hostname) >= 0;
        var $ = function (id) { return document.getElementById(id); };
        var nf = new Intl.NumberFormat('ko-KR');
        var esc = function (s) { return String(s).replace(/[&<>"]/g, function (c) { return { '&': '&amp;', '<': '&lt;', '>': '&gt;', '"': '&quot;' }[c]; }); };
        if (isLocal) $('localNote').hidden = false;

        /* ---------- 인증 ---------- */
        function saved() { return sessionStorage.getItem(KEY) || ''; }
        function hdrs() { return { 'x-admin-key': saved() }; }
        function showShell() { $('login').hidden = true; $('shell').hidden = false; }
        function showLogin() { $('shell').hidden = true; $('login').hidden = false; }
        $('loginForm').addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
          e.preventDefault();
          var pw = $('pw').value.trim();
          if (!pw && !isLocal) return;
          sessionStorage.setItem(KEY, pw || 'local');
          $('loginErr').hidden = true;
          boot();
        });
        $('logout').addEventListener('click', function () { sessionStorage.removeItem(KEY); showLogin(); });

        /* ---------- 탭 ---------- */
        var views = ['dashboard', 'content', 'stats'];
        document.querySelectorAll('.tabs .tab').forEach(function (b) {
          b.addEventListener('click', function () {
            document.querySelectorAll('.tabs .tab').forEach(function (x) { x.classList.remove('active'); });
            b.classList.add('active');
            views.forEach(function (v) { $('view-' + v).hidden = v !== b.dataset.view; });
            if (b.dataset.view === 'content' && !contentLoaded) loadPosts();
          });
        });

        /* ---------- 통계 데이터 ---------- */
        var statsCache = {};
        async function fetchStats(days) {
          if (statsCache[days]) return statsCache[days];
          if (isLocal) { statsCache[days] = mock(days); statsCache[days].sample = true; return statsCache[days]; }
          var res = await fetch('/api/stats?days=' + days, { headers: hdrs() });
          if (res.status === 401) throw { auth: true };
          if (!res.ok) throw new Error('stats ' + res.status);
          statsCache[days] = await res.json();
          return statsCache[days];
        }
        async function boot() {
          try {
            var d = await fetchStats(365);
            showShell(); $('sampleBadge').hidden = !d.sample;
            renderDashboard(d); renderStats(await fetchStats(30));
          } catch (err) {
            if (isLocal) { var m = mock(365); m.sample = true; showShell(); $('sampleBadge').hidden = false; renderDashboard(m); renderStats(mock(30)); return; }
            showLogin(); $('loginErr').hidden = false;
          }
        }

        function kstToday(off) { return new Date(Date.now() + 9 * 3600 * 1000 - (off || 0) * 86400000).toISOString().slice(0, 10); }
        function renderDashboard(d) {
          var byDay = d.byDay || [], map = {};
          byDay.forEach(function (r) { map[r.day] = r; });
          var t = map[kstToday(0)] || { views: 0, visitors: 0 }, y = map[kstToday(1)] || { views: 0, visitors: 0 };
          $('dToday').textContent = nf.format(t.views); $('dYesterday').textContent = nf.format(y.views);
          $('dTotal').textContent = nf.format((d.totals && d.totals.views) || 0);
          $('dVToday').textContent = nf.format(t.visitors); $('dVYesterday').textContent = nf.format(y.visitors);
          $('dVTotal').textContent = nf.format((d.totals && d.totals.visitors) || 0);
          $('dSubs').textContent = nf.format(d.subscribers || 0);
          chart($('dChart'), byDay.slice(-30));
          var total = (d.totals && d.totals.views) || 0, top = (d.topPaths || []).slice(0, 10);
          $('dTopPosts').innerHTML = top.length ? top.map(function (r, i) {
            return '<li><span class="rank">' + (i + 1) + '</span><a href="' + esc(r.path) + '" target="_blank" title="' + esc(r.path) + '">' + esc(prettyPath(r.path)) + '</a><span class="lval">' + nf.format(r.views) + '</span></li>';
          }).join('') : '<p class="muted small">데이터가 아직 없습니다.</p>';
          barsList($('dRefTypes'), (d.refTypes || []).map(mapType), total);
          rowsList($('dTopRef'), d.topRef || [], 'referrer', 'views');
        }
        function prettyPath(p) { return p === '/' ? '홈' : p.replace(/^\/blog\//, '').replace(/\/$/, '') || p; }

        document.querySelectorAll('.range button').forEach(function (b) {
          b.addEventListener('click', async function () {
            document.querySelectorAll('.range button').forEach(function (x) { x.classList.remove('active'); });
            b.classList.add('active'); renderStats(await fetchStats(parseInt(b.dataset.days, 10)));
          });
        });
        function renderStats(d) {
          $('rangeLabel').textContent = d.since + ' ~ 오늘';
          var views = (d.totals && d.totals.views) || 0, visitors = (d.totals && d.totals.visitors) || 0;
          $('kViews').textContent = nf.format(views); $('kVisitors').textContent = nf.format(visitors);
          $('kAvg').textContent = nf.format(Math.round(visitors / d.days)); $('kPer').textContent = visitors ? (views / visitors).toFixed(1) : '0';
          chart($('chart'), d.byDay || []);
          rowsList($('paths'), d.topPaths || [], 'path', 'views');
          barsList($('refTypes'), (d.refTypes || []).map(mapType), views);
          rowsList($('topRef'), d.topRef || [], 'referrer', 'views');
          barsList($('devices'), (d.devices || []).map(function (x) { return { label: devLabel(x.device), views: x.views }; }), views);
          rowsList($('countries'), (d.countries || []).map(function (x) { return { path: flag(x.country) + ' ' + x.country, views: x.views }; }), 'path', 'views');
        }
        function chart(el, byDay) {
          if (!byDay.length) { el.innerHTML = '<p class="muted small">데이터가 아직 없습니다.</p>'; return; }
          var max = Math.max.apply(null, byDay.map(function (r) { return r.views; })) || 1;
          var gap = 1, bw = (100 - gap * (byDay.length - 1)) / byDay.length;
          var bars = byDay.map(function (r, i) {
            var h = (r.views / max) * 88, x = i * (bw + gap);
            return '<rect x="' + x.toFixed(2) + '" y="' + (92 - h).toFixed(2) + '" width="' + bw.toFixed(2) + '" height="' + h.toFixed(2) + '" rx="0.4" fill="var(--brand)"><title>' + r.day + ' · ' + nf.format(r.views) + 'PV / ' + nf.format(r.visitors) + '명</title></rect>';
          }).join('');
          el.innerHTML = '<svg viewBox="0 0 100 96" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="svg">' + bars + '</svg><div class="axis"><span>' + byDay[0].day.slice(5) + '</span><span>' + byDay[byDay.length - 1].day.slice(5) + '</span></div>';
        }
        function rowsList(el, arr, kk, vk) {
          if (!arr.length) { el.innerHTML = '<p class="muted small">없음</p>'; return; }
          var max = Math.max.apply(null, arr.map(function (r) { return r[vk]; })) || 1;
          el.innerHTML = arr.map(function (r) {
            var w = Math.max(3, (r[vk] / max) * 100);
            return '<div class="lrow"><div class="lfill" style="width:' + w + '%"></div><span class="lkey" title="' + esc(r[kk]) + '">' + esc(r[kk]) + '</span><span class="lval">' + nf.format(r[vk]) + '</span></div>';
          }).join('');
        }
        function barsList(el, arr, total) {
          if (!arr.length) { el.innerHTML = '<p class="muted small">없음</p>'; return; }
          el.innerHTML = arr.map(function (r) {
            var pct = total ? Math.round((r.views / total) * 100) : 0;
            return '<div class="brow"><span class="blabel">' + esc(r.label) + '</span><span class="btrack"><span class="bfill" style="width:' + pct + '%"></span></span><span class="bval">' + pct + '%</span></div>';
          }).join('');
        }
        function mapType(x) { var m = { direct: '직접 방문', search: '검색', social: '소셜', referral: '외부 링크' }; return { label: m[x.type] || x.type, views: x.views }; }
        function devLabel(d) { return { mobile: '모바일', desktop: '데스크톱', tablet: '태블릿' }[d] || d; }
        function flag(cc) { if (!cc || cc.length !== 2) return '🌐'; return cc.replace(/./g, function (c) { return String.fromCodePoint(127397 + c.charCodeAt(0)); }); }

        /* ═══════════ 콘텐츠 관리 ═══════════ */
        var contentLoaded = false, currentSha = null, currentSlug = null, pvOn = true, pvTimer = null;

        var allPosts = [];
        async function loadPosts() {
          contentLoaded = true;
          if (isLocal) { $('contentNote').hidden = false; $('postList').innerHTML = ''; return; }
          $('postList').innerHTML = '<p class="muted small pad">불러오는 중…</p>';
          try {
            var res = await fetch('/api/posts', { headers: hdrs() });
            if (!res.ok) throw new Error((await res.json()).error || res.status);
            var data = await res.json();
            allPosts = data.posts || [];
            var pub = allPosts.filter(function (p) { return !p.draft; }).length;
            $('postCount').textContent = allPosts.length + '개 (발행 ' + pub + ' · 초안 ' + (allPosts.length - pub) + ')';
            renderList($('postSearch').value);
          } catch (e) {
            $('postList').innerHTML = '<p class="err pad">목록을 불러오지 못했습니다: ' + esc(e.message || e) + '<br>GITHUB_TOKEN 설정을 확인하세요 (docs/analytics-admin.md).</p>';
          }
        }
        function renderList(q) {
          q = (q || '').toLowerCase().trim();
          var list = allPosts.filter(function (p) {
            return !q || (p.title || '').toLowerCase().indexOf(q) >= 0 || p.slug.toLowerCase().indexOf(q) >= 0;
          });
          if (!list.length) { $('postList').innerHTML = '<p class="muted small pad">' + (q ? '검색 결과가 없습니다.' : '글이 없습니다.') + '</p>'; return; }
          $('postList').innerHTML = list.map(function (p) {
            var date = (p.slug.match(/^(\d{4}-\d{2}-\d{2})/) || [])[1] || '';
            var badge = p.draft ? '<span class="pbadge draft">초안</span>' : '<span class="pbadge pub">발행</span>';
            var cat = p.tag ? '#' + esc(p.tag) : '<span class="pr-nocat">카테고리 없음</span>';
            return '<button class="post-row" data-slug="' + esc(p.slug) + '">' +
              '<div class="pr-body">' +
                '<div class="pr-titleline">' + badge + '<span class="pr-title">' + esc(p.title || p.slug) + '</span></div>' +
                '<div class="pr-meta"><span class="pr-cat">' + cat + '</span><span class="pr-dot">·</span><span>' + date + '</span><span class="pr-dot">·</span><span class="pr-file">' + esc(p.slug) + '</span></div>' +
              '</div>' +
              '<span class="pr-edit">편집 ✎</span></button>';
          }).join('');
          document.querySelectorAll('.post-row').forEach(function (b) { b.addEventListener('click', function () { openEditor(b.dataset.slug); }); });
        }
        var _searchT = null;
        $('postSearch').addEventListener('input', function () { var v = this.value; clearTimeout(_searchT); _searchT = setTimeout(function () { renderList(v); }, 150); });

        async function openEditor(slug) {
          $('postList').hidden = true; $('editor').hidden = false; $('edMsg').hidden = true;
          $('edTitle').textContent = '글 편집'; $('edSlug').textContent = slug;
          $('edBody').value = '불러오는 중…'; currentSlug = slug; currentSha = null;
          try {
            var res = await fetch('/api/posts/' + encodeURIComponent(slug), { headers: hdrs() });
            if (!res.ok) throw new Error((await res.json()).error || res.status);
            var data = await res.json();
            currentSha = data.sha; $('edBody').value = data.content;
            $('edDelete').hidden = false;
            refreshAll();
          } catch (e) { $('edBody').value = ''; msg('불러오기 실패: ' + (e.message || e), true); }
        }
        $('edDelete').addEventListener('click', async function () {
          if (!currentSlug || !currentSha) { msg('저장된 글에만 삭제가 가능합니다.', true); return; }
          if (!confirm('정말 삭제할까요? 되돌릴 수 없습니다.\n\n' + currentSlug)) return;
          $('edDelete').disabled = true; msg('삭제 중…', false);
          try {
            var res = await fetch('/api/posts/' + encodeURIComponent(currentSlug) + '?sha=' + encodeURIComponent(currentSha), { method: 'DELETE', headers: hdrs() });
            var data = await res.json();
            if (!res.ok) throw new Error(data.detail || data.error || res.status);
            contentLoaded = false; closeEditor(); loadPosts();
          } catch (e) { msg('삭제 실패: ' + (e.message || e), true); }
          finally { $('edDelete').disabled = false; }
        });
        function closeEditor() { $('editor').hidden = true; $('postList').hidden = false; currentSlug = null; currentSha = null; }
        $('edCancel').addEventListener('click', closeEditor);

        /* frontmatter / 본문 분리 */
        function splitDoc(text) {
          var m = text.match(/^---\n([\s\S]*?)\n---\n?([\s\S]*)$/);
          if (m) return { fm: m[1], body: m[2] };
          return { fm: '', body: text };
        }
        function fmField(fm, key) {
          var m = fm.match(new RegExp('^' + key + ':\\s*(.+)$', 'm'));
          return m ? m[1].replace(/^['"]|['"]$/g, '').trim() : '';
        }

        /* 글자수 + SEO 힌트 + 제목 */
        function refreshCounts() {
          var d = splitDoc($('edBody').value);
          var n = d.body.replace(/^\s+/, '').length;
          var title = fmField(d.fm, 'title'), desc = fmField(d.fm, 'description');
          var tl = title.length, dl = desc.length;
          var draft = /^draft:\s*true/m.test(d.fm);
          if (title) $('edTitle').textContent = title;
          $('edDraft').textContent = draft ? '● 초안' : '○ 발행상태';
          $('edDraft').className = 'btn-utility ' + (draft ? 'is-draft' : 'is-pub');
          function tag(label, val, lo, hi) {
            var ok = val >= lo && val <= hi;
            return '<span class="' + (val === 0 ? '' : ok ? 'ok' : 'warn') + '">' + label + ' ' + val + '</span>';
          }
          $('seoHints').innerHTML = tag('제목', tl, 20, 45) + tag('설명', dl, 80, 160) + tag('본문', n, 2250, 2750).replace(String(n), nf.format(n) + '자');
        }

        /* 미리보기 렌더 (marked + mermaid) */
        function renderPreview() {
          if (!pvOn) return;
          var d = splitDoc($('edBody').value);
          var el = $('edPreview');
          if (!window.marked) { el.innerHTML = '<p class="muted small">미리보기 로딩 중…</p>'; return; }
          try { el.innerHTML = window.marked.parse(d.body, { gfm: true, breaks: false }); }
          catch (e) { el.innerHTML = '<p class="err small">미리보기 오류</p>'; return; }
          // ```mermaid → <pre class="mermaid"> 후 렌더
          var blocks = el.querySelectorAll('code.language-mermaid');
          if (blocks.length) {
            blocks.forEach(function (c) {
              var pre = document.createElement('pre'); pre.className = 'mermaid'; pre.textContent = c.textContent;
              c.parentNode.replaceWith(pre);
            });
            import('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid@11/dist/mermaid.esm.min.mjs')
              .then(function (m) { m.default.initialize({ startOnLoad: false, securityLevel: 'strict', theme: 'neutral' }); return m.default.run({ querySelector: '#edPreview pre.mermaid' }); })
              .catch(function () {});
          }
        }
        function refreshAll() { refreshCounts(); renderPreview(); }
        $('edBody').addEventListener('input', function () {
          refreshCounts();
          clearTimeout(pvTimer); pvTimer = setTimeout(renderPreview, 350);
        });

        /* 미리보기 토글 */
        $('edPvToggle').addEventListener('click', function () {
          pvOn = !pvOn;
          $('edSplit').classList.toggle('no-preview', !pvOn);
          $('edPvToggle').textContent = pvOn ? '미리보기' : '미리보기 켜기';
          if (pvOn) renderPreview();
        });

        /* 초안/발행 토글 */
        $('edDraft').addEventListener('click', function () {
          var v = $('edBody').value;
          if (/^draft:\s*true/m.test(v)) v = v.replace(/^draft:\s*true/m, 'draft: false');
          else if (/^draft:\s*false/m.test(v)) v = v.replace(/^draft:\s*false/m, 'draft: true');
          else { msg('frontmatter에 draft 항목이 없습니다.', true); return; }
          $('edBody').value = v; refreshCounts();
          msg('상태를 바꿨습니다. 저장해야 반영됩니다.', false);
        });

        /* 툴바 서식 삽입 */
        var TEMPLATES = {
          table: '\n| 항목 | 설명 |\n| --- | --- |\n| A | 내용 |\n| B | 내용 |\n',
          mermaid: '\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n  A[시작] --> B{판단}\n  B -->|예| C[실행]\n  B -->|아니오| D[보류]\n```\n',
        };
        function surround(before, after, placeholder) {
          var ta = $('edBody'), s = ta.selectionStart, e = ta.selectionEnd, v = ta.value;
          var sel = v.slice(s, e) || placeholder || '';
          var out = v.slice(0, s) + before + sel + after + v.slice(e);
          ta.value = out; ta.focus();
          ta.selectionStart = s + before.length; ta.selectionEnd = s + before.length + sel.length;
          refreshAll();
        }
        function insertBlock(text) {
          var ta = $('edBody'), s = ta.selectionStart, v = ta.value;
          ta.value = v.slice(0, s) + text + v.slice(s); ta.focus();
          ta.selectionStart = ta.selectionEnd = s + text.length; refreshAll();
        }
        document.querySelector('.toolbar').addEventListener('click', function (ev) {
          var b = ev.target.closest('button[data-md]'); if (!b) return;
          var k = b.dataset.md;
          if (k === 'h2') surround('\n## ', '\n', '제목');
          else if (k === 'h3') surround('\n### ', '\n', '소제목');
          else if (k === 'bold') surround('**', '**', '굵게');
          else if (k === 'italic') surround('*', '*', '기울임');
          else if (k === 'link') surround('[', '](https://)', '링크텍스트');
          else if (k === 'ul') surround('\n- ', '', '항목');
          else if (k === 'quote') surround('\n> ', '\n', '인용');
          else if (k === 'code') surround('`', '`', '코드');
          else if (k === 'table') insertBlock(TEMPLATES.table);
          else if (k === 'mermaid') insertBlock(TEMPLATES.mermaid);
        });

        /* 이미지 업로드 (드래그앤드롭 / 붙여넣기 → GitHub 커밋) */
        var _uid = 0;
        async function uploadImage(file) {
          var ta = $('edBody');
          var token = '![업로드 중… ' + (++_uid) + ']()';
          var pos = ta.selectionStart;
          ta.value = ta.value.slice(0, pos) + token + ta.value.slice(pos);
          refreshAll();
          try {
            var fd = new FormData();
            fd.append('file', file, file.name || 'image.png');
            var res = await fetch('/api/upload', { method: 'POST', headers: hdrs(), body: fd });
            var data = await res.json();
            if (!res.ok) throw new Error(data.detail || data.error || res.status);
            var alt = (file.name || 'image').replace(/\.[^.]+$/, '');
            ta.value = ta.value.replace(token, '![' + alt + '](' + data.url + ')');
            msg('✅ 이미지 업로드됨 (다음 배포 시 반영): ' + data.url, false);
          } catch (e) {
            ta.value = ta.value.replace(token, '');
            msg('이미지 업로드 실패: ' + (e.message || e), true);
          }
          refreshAll();
        }
        (function () {
          var ta = $('edBody');
          ta.addEventListener('dragover', function (e) { if (e.dataTransfer && [].some.call(e.dataTransfer.items || [], function (it) { return it.kind === 'file'; })) { e.preventDefault(); ta.classList.add('dragover'); } });
          ta.addEventListener('dragleave', function () { ta.classList.remove('dragover'); });
          ta.addEventListener('drop', function (e) {
            var files = e.dataTransfer && e.dataTransfer.files;
            var imgs = files ? [].filter.call(files, function (f) { return /^image\//.test(f.type); }) : [];
            if (!imgs.length) return;
            e.preventDefault(); ta.classList.remove('dragover');
            if (isLocal) { msg('로컬 미리보기에서는 업로드를 사용할 수 없습니다.', true); return; }
            imgs.forEach(uploadImage);
          });
          ta.addEventListener('paste', function (e) {
            var items = (e.clipboardData && e.clipboardData.items) || [];
            var handled = false;
            for (var i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {
              if (items[i].type && items[i].type.indexOf('image/') === 0) {
                var f = items[i].getAsFile();
                if (f) { handled = true; if (isLocal) msg('로컬 미리보기에서는 업로드를 사용할 수 없습니다.', true); else uploadImage(f); }
              }
            }
            if (handled) e.preventDefault();
          });
        })();

        /* 저장 */
        $('edSave').addEventListener('click', async function () {
          if (!currentSlug) return;
          var content = $('edBody').value;
          if (content.trim().length < 10) { msg('내용이 비어 있습니다.', true); return; }
          $('edSave').disabled = true; msg('저장 중…', false);
          try {
            var res = await fetch('/api/posts/' + encodeURIComponent(currentSlug), {
              method: 'PUT', headers: Object.assign({ 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, hdrs()),
              body: JSON.stringify({ content: content, sha: currentSha }),
            });
            var data = await res.json();
            if (!res.ok) throw new Error(data.detail || data.error || res.status);
            currentSha = data.sha;
            msg('✅ GitHub에 저장됨 (커밋 ' + data.commit.slice(0, 7) + '). 사이트 반영은 배포 시 적용.', false);
            contentLoaded = false;
          } catch (e) { msg('저장 실패: ' + (e.message || e), true); }
          finally { $('edSave').disabled = false; }
        });

        /* 새 글 */
        $('newPost').addEventListener('click', function () {
          if (isLocal) { alert('로컬 미리보기에서는 사용할 수 없습니다.'); return; }
          var today = kstToday(0);
          var slug = prompt('파일명(슬러그). 예: ' + today + '-my-post.md', today + '-.md');
          if (!slug) return;
          if (!/\.(md|mdx)$/.test(slug)) slug += '.md';
          currentSlug = slug; currentSha = null;
          $('postList').hidden = true; $('editor').hidden = false; $('edTitle').textContent = '새 글';
          $('edSlug').textContent = slug; $('edMsg').hidden = true; $('edDelete').hidden = true;
          $('edBody').value = ['---', 'title: 제목을 입력하세요', 'description: 검색 결과에 노출될 한 줄 요약 (120~160자)', 'pubDate: ' + today, "tags: ['코칭']", 'keywords: []', 'tldr: 핵심 한 줄 요약', 'draft: true', '---', '', '여기에 본문을 씁니다. (목표: 2,500자 내외)', ''].join('\n');
          refreshAll();
        });

        function msg(text, isErr) { var el = $('edMsg'); el.hidden = false; el.textContent = text; el.className = isErr ? 'err small' : 'ok-msg small'; }

        /* ---------- 로컬 샘플 ---------- */
        function mock(n) {
          var byDay = [], views = 0, visitors = 0, today = new Date();
          for (var i = n - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            var dt = new Date(today.getTime() - i * 86400000);
            var v = 20 + Math.round(Math.random() * 60), u = Math.round(v * 0.65);
            byDay.push({ day: dt.toISOString().slice(0, 10), views: v, visitors: u }); views += v; visitors += u;
          }
          return { days: n, since: byDay[0].day, totals: { views: views, visitors: visitors }, subscribers: Math.round(visitors * 0.03), byDay: byDay,
            topPaths: [{ path: '/blog/2026-07-02-ai-coaching-90-percent', views: Math.round(views * 0.2) }, { path: '/', views: Math.round(views * 0.18) }, { path: '/blog/2026-07-01-ai-customer-tone', views: Math.round(views * 0.15) }, { path: '/blog', views: Math.round(views * 0.11) }, { path: '/about', views: Math.round(views * 0.06) }],
            refTypes: [{ type: 'search', views: Math.round(views * 0.42) }, { type: 'direct', views: Math.round(views * 0.3) }, { type: 'social', views: Math.round(views * 0.2) }, { type: 'referral', views: Math.round(views * 0.08) }],
            topRef: [{ referrer: 'google.com', views: Math.round(views * 0.26) }, { referrer: 'naver.com', views: Math.round(views * 0.15) }, { referrer: 'linkedin.com', views: Math.round(views * 0.1) }],
            countries: [{ country: 'KR', views: Math.round(views * 0.87) }, { country: 'US', views: Math.round(views * 0.06) }],
            devices: [{ device: 'mobile', views: Math.round(views * 0.57) }, { device: 'desktop', views: Math.round(views * 0.37) }, { device: 'tablet', views: Math.round(views * 0.06) }] };
        }

        if (saved() || isLocal) boot();
      })();
    </script>

    <style is:global>
      /* admin은 독립 페이지 — JS로 동적 생성되는 요소(글 목록·통계 막대 등)에도
         스타일이 적용되도록 전역 스타일 사용. (스코프 CSS는 innerHTML 요소에 안 붙음) */
      body { background: var(--bg); }
      [hidden] { display: none !important; }
      .muted { color: var(--text-muted); }
      .small { font-size: 0.85rem; }
      .err { color: #d33; font-size: 0.88rem; }
      .ok-msg { color: var(--sticker-green); }
      .pad { padding: 1rem; }

      .login { min-height: 100vh; display: grid; place-items: center; padding: 20px; }
      .login .card { width: 100%; max-width: 360px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--rounded-xl); padding: 2.2rem 1.8rem; box-shadow: var(--shadow); text-align: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.7rem; }
      .login .dot { width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--brand); box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px var(--brand-soft); margin: 0 auto 0.4rem; }
      .login h1 { font-size: 1.4rem; }
      .login input { padding: 0.7em 0.9em; border-radius: var(--rounded-xs); border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-size: 1rem; font-family: inherit; }
      .login input:focus { outline: 2px solid var(--brand); border-color: var(--brand); }

      .topbar { position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 40; background: var(--surface); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .topbar .inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 56px; gap: 1rem; }
      .topbar .left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.4rem; min-width: 0; }
      .brand { font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -0.02em; white-space: nowrap; }
      .brand .ext { color: var(--text-faint); font-size: 0.8em; }
      .tabs { display: flex; gap: 4px; }
      .tabs .tab { border: 0; background: transparent; font: inherit; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.94rem; color: var(--text-muted); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 9999px; cursor: pointer; }
      .tabs .tab.active { background: var(--brand); color: #fff; }
      .tabs .tab:not(.active):hover { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); }
      .topbar .right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.7rem; }
      .badge { font-size: 0.7rem; background: var(--brand-soft); color: var(--brand); padding: 0.25em 0.7em; border-radius: 9999px; font-weight: 700; }
      .btn-utility { cursor: pointer; }

      .view { padding-top: 24px; }
      .kpis { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      .kpi { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--rounded-lg); padding: 16px 18px; }
      .k-label { display: block; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.35em; }
      .k-val { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
      .panel { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--rounded-lg); padding: 20px 22px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      .panel h2 { font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
      .panel h3.sub { margin: 20px 0 10px; font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
      .grid2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
      @media (max-width: 760px) { .grid2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
      .chart .svg { width: 100%; height: 150px; display: block; }
      .axis { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; color: var(--text-faint); font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 6px; }
      .lrow { position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 7px 9px; border-radius: var(--rounded-md); overflow: hidden; }
      .lrow + .lrow { margin-top: 3px; }
      .lfill { position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; background: var(--brand-soft); }
      .lkey { position: relative; flex: 1; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; font-size: 0.9rem; }
      .lval { position: relative; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.88rem; padding-left: 0.6em; }
      .brow { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 9px; }
      .blabel { width: 5.5em; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
      .btrack { flex: 1; height: 8px; background: var(--code-bg); border-radius: 9999px; overflow: hidden; }
      .bfill { display: block; height: 100%; background: var(--brand); border-radius: 9999px; }
      .bval { width: 3em; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; }
      .ranklist { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      .ranklist li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 8px 4px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .ranklist li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      .rank { width: 1.5em; text-align: center; font-weight: 700; color: var(--brand); font-size: 0.9rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
      .ranklist a { flex: 1; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.92rem; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
      .ranklist a:hover { color: var(--brand); }

      .content-head, .stats-head { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .content-head h2, .stats-head h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; }
      .content-tools { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
      #postSearch { padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 9999px; background: var(--surface); color: var(--text); font: inherit; font-size: 0.88rem; min-width: 180px; }
      #postSearch:focus { outline: 2px solid var(--brand); border-color: var(--brand); }
      .pbadge { flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 9999px; }
      .pbadge.draft { background: var(--brand-soft); color: var(--sticker-orange); }
      .pbadge.pub { background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sticker-green) 15%, transparent); color: var(--sticker-green); }
      .btn-utility.danger { color: #d33; border-color: color-mix(in srgb, #d33 40%, var(--border)); }
      .btn-utility.danger:hover { background: color-mix(in srgb, #d33 8%, transparent); }
      .small-btn { font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 0.5em 1.1em; }
      .postlist { padding: 0; overflow: hidden; }
      .post-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; width: 100%; text-align: left; border: 0; background: transparent; font: inherit; padding: 15px 20px; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); transition: background 0.12s ease; }
      .post-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      .post-row:hover { background: var(--bg); }
      .pr-body { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
      .pr-titleline { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
      .pr-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.02rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
      .pr-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; color: var(--text-faint); font-size: 0.82rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .pr-cat { color: var(--brand); font-weight: 500; }
      .pr-nocat { color: var(--text-faint); font-weight: 400; }
      .pr-dot { opacity: 0.5; }
      .pr-file { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace; opacity: 0.75; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; max-width: 16em; }
      .pr-edit { flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; }
      .post-row:hover .pr-edit { color: var(--brand); }

      /* 에디터 */
      .editor-head { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 10px; }
      .editor-head h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
      .editor-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .seohints { display: inline-flex; gap: 8px; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-faint); margin-right: 4px; }
      .seohints .ok { color: var(--sticker-green); font-weight: 600; }
      .seohints .warn { color: var(--sticker-orange); font-weight: 600; }
      .btn-utility.is-draft { color: var(--sticker-orange); border-color: var(--sticker-orange); }
      .btn-utility.is-pub { color: var(--sticker-green); border-color: var(--sticker-green); }
      .toolbar { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; align-items: center; padding: 6px; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--rounded-md) var(--rounded-md) 0 0; border-bottom: none; }
      .toolbar button { border: 0; background: transparent; font: inherit; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: var(--rounded-xs); cursor: pointer; }
      .toolbar button:hover { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); }
      .tb-sep { width: 1px; height: 18px; background: var(--border); margin: 0 4px; }
      .split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0 0 var(--rounded-lg) var(--rounded-lg); overflow: hidden; }
      .split.no-preview { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .split.no-preview .preview { display: none; }
      #edBody { width: 100%; min-height: 64vh; resize: vertical; background: var(--surface); color: var(--text); border: 0; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 18px 20px; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.7; }
      #edBody:focus { outline: none; }
      #edBody.dragover { outline: 2px dashed var(--brand); outline-offset: -4px; background: var(--brand-soft); }
      .preview { min-height: 64vh; max-height: 80vh; overflow-y: auto; padding: 18px 22px; background: var(--bg); font-size: 1rem; }
      .preview > :first-child { margin-top: 0; }
      @media (max-width: 820px) { .split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .preview { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); } }

      .range { display: inline-flex; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 9999px; overflow: hidden; }
      .range button { border: 0; background: transparent; padding: 6px 14px; font: inherit; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); cursor: pointer; }
      .range button.active { background: var(--brand); color: #fff; }
      .foot { padding: 24px; }
      @media (max-width: 640px) { .topbar .inner { height: auto; padding-block: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; } .tabs .tab { padding: 8px 14px; } }
    </style>
  </body>
